In the spirit of the decentralized digital future that this creator
believes in — this is open source.

All of it: the How to Save the World application AND the NeuroVerse OS
cognitive engine beneath it (Eight-Box Scaffold, Echelon Core
Intelligence, Operator Model, Mission Engine, State Engine, Mode
Engine, ACE Loader, Archetype System). One repo, one license, no
asterisks.

If this work fuels yours, fuel it back:
https://howtosavetheworld.info/support

